    "cancer samples from different sources) closer to each other, while moving samples with different labels (e.g.",
    "cancer samples from non-cancer samples) further apart:",
    "where α is a hyperparameter that enforces what should be the minimum difference of distances between a sample and its positive and negative anchors in the latent space, and it is set to α = 1.",
